actions.message:
__**Report**__
Report system based on multiple channels that store the reports info, when you report someone a embed is sent to the reports channel with a custom ID, staff can accept or deny it and the info stores in the accepted or denied reports channel.
`!help report`
__**Warn**__
Staff can warn people that are against the rules, if someone reach 3 warns will get muted and if you are muted you can appeal. Warnings are stored in the staff register channel.
`!help warn`
__**Mute**__
Staff members can mute someone permanently or temporarily.
`!help mute`
__**Ban**__
When staff ban someone a embed is sent in the same channel where you banned someone and the bans are stored in the staff register channel.
`!help ban`
__**Send**__
The send command allows the command triggerer send custom embeds with colors, pictures and more.
`!help send`
__**Say**__
With this command you can send messages as if you were the bot.
`!help say`
__**Clear**__
Some staff members can clean the chat removing messages with manage messages permission.
`!help clear`
__**Discord Status**__
You can check discord servers status.
`!status`
__**Info**__
Use it to know other people's usefull information.
